sentences: Justin Ritter (born September 28, 1987), known professionally as SwizZz, is an American rapper and songwriter.
He has released various singles and released two mixtapes including Haywire with Hopsin, and Good Morning SwizZzle.
After high school SwizZz got accepted into the University of California at Irvine, but after two years he decided to put his education on hold, while he would pursue a career in music.
